* Apache mods need to be enable
--------------
	- Expire
	- Rewrite
	- Deflate

* Some Package have to be installed via apt :
--------------

	+ PHP
	- php5
	- php-pear
	- php5-mysqli
	- php5-pgsql
	- php5-curl
	- php5-xmlrpc
	- php5-json
	- php5-memcache

	+ Services
	- gettext
	- imagemagick
	- memcached
	- pwgen
	- java 1.6

	+ Css compression
	- csstidy

* Some Package have to be installed via pecl :
--------------

	+ PHP
	- apc

* Locales need to be available on system
--------------

	+ linux locale
	- bg_BG.UTF-8
	- de_DE.UTF-8
	- en_GB.UTF-8
	- en_US.UTF-8
	- es_ES.UTF-8
	- fr_FR.UTF-8
	- it_IT.UTF-8
	- ru_RU.UTF-8

